```plantuml
@startuml i5ting_stuq-koa

actor User
participant "Koa Application" as KoaApp
participant "Middleware Stack" as Middleware
participant "Route Handler" as Route
participant "Database (MongoDB)" as DB

User -> KoaApp: HTTP Request
activate KoaApp

KoaApp -> Middleware: Process request through middleware
activate Middleware
Middleware -> Middleware: Execute middleware functions
Middleware --> KoaApp: Modified context
deactivate Middleware

KoaApp -> Route: Route matching
activate Route
Route -> DB: Database query (if needed)
activate DB
DB --> Route: Query results
deactivate DB
Route --> KoaApp: Response data
deactivate Route

KoaApp --> User: HTTP Response
deactivate KoaApp

@enduml
```